title: Charlotte activists met the immigration crackdown with ‘bless your heart’ resistance
summary: ICE and CBP's operations in North Carolina were challenged by a network of thousands of volunteers who formed an early-warning system. This grassroots effort aimed to alert communities about potential immigration enforcement activities. The initiative highlights the growing resistance and community organization against federal immigration enforcement in the region.

title: Verstappen back in F1 title race after Norris and Piastri disqualification follows his Las Vegas win
summary: Max Verstappen fell 24 points behind Lando Norris in the standings due to significant wear on the skid blocks of his McLaren. As a result, both he and teammate Oscar Piastri ended the race without earning any points. The wear on the skid blocks significantly impacted their performance.
